articles.title: JetBrains AI Assistant Reaches General Availability
articles.content: JetBrains AI Assistant becomes generally available with the 2023.3 release, supporting over 20 programming languages across all JetBrains IDEs.
articles.summary: JetBrains AI Assistant becomes generally available with the 2023.3 release, supporting over 20 programming languages across all JetBrains IDEs....

articles.title: Amazon Q Developer Launches in Preview at AWS re:Invent
articles.content: Amazon Web Services unveiled Amazon Q Developer at re:Invent 2023, introducing an AI-powered coding assistant designed to help developers with code generation, debugging, and AWS-specific tasks.
articles.summary: Amazon Web Services unveiled Amazon Q Developer at re:Invent 2023, introducing an AI-powered coding assistant designed to help developers with code generation, debugging, and AWS-specific tasks....
